Subject: Bouncing Bus

Also check that your springplate bushings are in good shape. Stiffer shocks
will help, but you should be able to run normal oil filled shocks without
"the bounce". Stock rubber would be sufficient, but if you go with urethane,
make sure you use the supplied lube to make sure they don't squeak.

Eric Allred
64 Bus
